When you check your supply chain,

00:39:43.113 --> 00:39:47.183
you stop broken
plugins or sketchy themes

00:39:47.184 --> 00:39:49.420
before they ever reach production.

00:39:49.787 --> 00:39:53.122
When you add CI gates,
accessibility becomes part

00:39:53.123 --> 00:39:55.892
of your normal quality checks,

00:39:55.893 --> 00:39:58.429
right next to performance
and security.

00:39:58.595 --> 00:40:00.663
Defense in Depth just means

00:40:00.664 --> 00:40:03.766
it's not one lonely checklist
at the end.

00:40:03.767 --> 00:40:06.703
It's built into every phase,

00:40:07.037 --> 00:40:12.776
into design and dev, QA,
content, all working together.

00:40:13.343 --> 00:40:15.912
Ownership is what keeps it alive.

